{"tid":1420002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"DLLM 和理非同我入撚曬黎","createTime":"2019-08-06T03:20:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T03:36:20.000Z","uid":296211,"like":24,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0cfc645223e0c832b3dff429a220337a3c535726","tid":1420002,"uid":296211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:20:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">呢期見到好多和理非同勇武割蓆post</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">割你老母啊！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">[size=4]我就由6月一直都係和理非黎嘅，從來冇諗過要割蓆啊！DLLM，口口聲聲要人互相尊重，你有冇係勇武巴打立場諗過啊？有冇聽過勇武爲矛，和理非為盾啊？人數越多越安全啊！你係唔係冇撚去發過夢啊？我次次發夢都好多野做！和理非唔係去行行企企，打個卡，一出黑旗就走左去啊！<br />\n<br />\n雖然我知道某部分勇武巴打真係好撚躁，好冇禮貌。我都有試過比個唔知頭唔知路嘅勇武巴話。但係咁又點啊？我從來都冇諗過要割蓆啊！做和理非，一係家庭有責任，一係就自之做勇武會拖後腳。但都係唔會影響我地同勇武嘅目標係一致啊！<br />\n<br />\n咩叫we connect 啊？有時我都發唔到夢啊！咁點啊？係屋企或都公司做文宣囉！唔係返到去就可以唔關你事啊！<br />\n<br />\n要記住，大家係互相配合，互相需要大家！冇勇武，我地唔可以做到今時今日咁。但勇武都需要我地後方支援！<br />\n<br />\n我都明白可能大家覺得和理非集會太少，次次最後都變勇武。咁我覺得大家可以商量下點搞啲真&middot;和理非行動，完左就散。咁先叫係兄弟爬山。唔係下下等人搞完黎參加，而係自己落手搞。一黎可以比勇武師兄抖下，二黎可以keep 住有野搞。例如機場集會，都係和理非主場。<br />\n<br />\n勇武巴，雖然知道你地日日可能4點幾先完場，又驚被拉，又或者親眼睇住朋友被拉好嬲。但希望你地攰可能真係抖下，我地大把路要行。同希望你地對和理非態度好啲，真心嘅。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求缺一不可！<br />\n不割蓆，不分化！</span></span>"},{"pid":"2288fa1e85e480d9981639f8dca23dae9542daf1","tid":1420002,"uid":296211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:21:04.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"5ba7b02546dc0683d679bcc39ecbb11b9085b9fe","tid":1420002,"uid":296211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:21:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a3250e67d6ea329d2fb3e17958d930ffae86e62f","tid":1420002,"uid":296211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:21:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a968fa2e059429ac791f0685d342741012c9e183","tid":1420002,"uid":296211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:21:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d4abb30a4339e200655f0d0d50c2f66d381ff4cd","tid":1420002,"uid":296211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:21:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9687468630e4ef4a5beae5f07f840832ecbe264a","tid":1420002,"uid":219120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:21:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2264cba68e46d1e5364426445227d2052cae6988","tid":1420002,"uid":296211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:22:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"488a71c18f2a54a0ab8b9b7d7f90b8d1b694d4b2","tid":1420002,"uid":296211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:22:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"75d5e74de029402bbf28e7118333b7a446dc0dee","tid":1420002,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:22:30.000Z","msg":"其實無割，只係檢討策略"},{"pid":"77c403faba264e8e56808d77640a1099fb85278c","tid":1420002,"uid":275588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:22:36.000Z","msg":"我係和理非<br />\n我唔割啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4251c25481ee4ac7a700218c5989565324b1026d","tid":1420002,"uid":268410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:22:47.000Z","msg":"放核彈都唔割"},{"pid":"664a2dc82f53a4c80783295d8665569d3fcd52c5","tid":1420002,"uid":296211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75d5e74de029402bbf28e7118333b7a446dc0dee","tid":1420002,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:22:30.000Z","msg":"其實無割，只係檢討策略"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:23:07.000Z","msg":"見到有個post話割，好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6db1e2add729870b2ada51016e4e4663a5220869","tid":1420002,"uid":294811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:23:13.000Z","msg":"唔割"},{"pid":"8e2195f92f33a386ab61894c604f5ad6391a5645","tid":1420002,"uid":203308,"like":0,"disli